node.text: Hey @thom_astro, I pulled 7.9g in my recent flight in a fighter jet. It was a bumpy ride at times but I'm definitely getting better and I'll keep training. Please call me when there is a spot in a @spacex rocket to the @iss (You can put me in the cargo bay if needed)

node.text:
Three weeks of intense training in Andorra came to an end today. I was able to combine road and mountain bikes and I'm satisfied with what I achieved. I'd like to thank my brother @jurajsagan for being my training partner, the @picmaiamountainhotel, Maros, Michael, and everybody else that helped me and supported me in Andorra. I'm heading now to Surhuisterveen for the start of the @beneluxtour. 

Trois semaines d'entraînement intensif en Andorre viennent de se terminer aujourd'hui. J'ai pu combiner vélo de route et VTT et je suis satisfait de ce que j'ai pu atteindre. Je voudrais remercier mon frère @jurajsagan d'être mon partenaire d'entraînement, le @picmaiamountainhotel, Maros, Michael et tous ceux qui m'ont aidé et soutenu en Andorre. Je prends la route maintenant vers Surhuisterveen pour le départ du @beneluxtour. 

@iamspecialized @sportful @ride100percent

(Photo @raymondkerckhoffs / @ridemagazinenl)
